=== Marriage to Elizabeth Kendrick? ===
The 10 Feb 1806 marriage bond for Elizabeth Kendrack shows the groom as "John Utz".  
* Closest in the 1810 census<ref></ref> is John Oatts, with 2 males under 10, 1 male 16-25, and 1 female 16-25.
* 1810 Personal Property Tax<ref>https://www.familysearch.org/ark:/61903/3:1:3Q9M-CS79-2HDB-B?cat=koha%3A695422&i=440&lang=en</ref> shows John Ortz ("of John") with 1 white male above 16; "John Otz" is crossed out with a note "see Utz".  "John Utz" shows 1 white male above 16.
* 1820 Personal Property Tax shows John Ort<ref>https://www.familysearch.org/ark:/61903/3:1:3Q9M-CS79-29H3-W?cat=koha%3A695422&i=90&lang=en</ref> and John Utz<ref>https://www.familysearch.org/ark:/61903/3:1:3Q9M-CS79-2941-N?cat=koha%3A695422&i=100&lang=en</ref>.  This is the year Nancy Urt married Moses Koontz.
* 1821 Personal Property Tax shows John Ort<ref>https://www.familysearch.org/ark:/61903/3:1:3Q9M-CS79-294D-Y?cat=koha%3A695422&i=170&lang=en</ref> and John Uttz<ref>https://www.familysearch.org/ark:/61903/3:1:3Q9M-CS79-294Z-K?cat=koha%3A695422&i=180&lang=en</ref>

The signature on the 1806 marriage bond was signed by the groom's own hand.  The signature in Nancy's 1820 was signed by the clerk and the bride's father's mark.

